{"tid":631179,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅巴2.0　椅背變薄增空間 LCD取代點陣式顯示屏","createTime":"2018-04-16T08:38:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T09:14:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"954fc17de6387eda9f753aef0a39acd0ead7c453","tid":631179,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T08:38:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180416/20362759?_ga=2.107733890.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180416%2F20362759%3F_ga%3D2.107733890.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=B3wWFzDYCiY6GGcomhzFmh4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=4facbdce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180416%2F20362759%3F_ga%3D2.107733890.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=1c399023\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180416/20362759?_ga=2.107733890.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n紅巴2.0　椅背變薄增空間<br />\nLCD取代點陣式顯示屏<br />\n<br />\n7.7K<br />\n港聞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【《蘋果》大馬直擊】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】九巴去年中推出新款「紅巴」，深受巴士迷熱捧。九巴早前完成紅巴設計改良，今年中再推新一批4部「紅巴2.0」投入服務。《蘋果》上周於馬來西亞新山的巴士製造廠直擊新紅巴真身。新車換上薄背座椅，腿部伸展空間略為增加；全車換上LCD顯示屏及動態路線顯示系統提供資訊。九巴指會因應乘客意見，考慮將新設備加裝到其他巴士。<br />\n<br />\n記者：鄭啟源<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180416/large/16la7p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180416%2Flarge%2F16la7p4.jpg&h=17bc80b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新紅巴車頂及上層地板的鋁板中，加入合成物料夾層。朱永倫攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180416/large/16la7p5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180416%2Flarge%2F16la7p5.jpg&h=db168028&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紅巴2.0<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180416/large/16la7p11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180416%2Flarge%2F16la7p11.jpg&h=1236882c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新座椅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新一批「紅巴2.0」由馬來西亞巴士製造商順豐客車（Gemilang）生產，其中3部採用富豪（Volvo）B9TL底盤，1部為德國猛獅（MAN）A95型號。巴士製作過程，從車身模板裝嵌、安裝底盤、鋪設線路及噴油等，可大致分為10個程序，需時個多月。4部新紅巴已全部完工，預料本月底送抵香港，待完成運輸署車型評定等測試後，今年中投入服務。<br />\n<br />\n新紅巴主要在車廂設備作出改良，九巴助理工程師譚崇輝指出，新巴士是特別訂做，車廠使用瑞士進口鋁材，車頂及上層地板的鋁板中，加入合成物料夾層，強度足以承受70名成人重量。上一代紅巴採用的座椅，突起的頭枕被乘客批評不夠舒適。<br />\n<br />\n譚指，新紅巴換上另一款意大利製座椅，座椅厚度較薄，乘客腿部伸展空間略為增加，頭枕設計亦改成沒有突起。不過，記者試坐時，發現因椅背變薄，後方乘客如以膝頭頂住前座椅背，前座乘客背部會明顯感受到後方施力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180416/large/16la7p10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180416%2Flarge%2F16la7p10.jpg&h=de9c88b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLCD屏<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180416/large/16la7p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180416%2Flarge%2F16la7p2.jpg&h=d1d38931&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n防撞墊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年料增460新巴士<br />\n<br />\n譚崇輝續指，車頭的九巴標誌亦裝有沁光燈，在夜間更突出。車頭、車尾，及車身的路線顯示牌，會全部轉用LCD顯示屏，較現時採用的點陣式顯示系統清晰；連接上層的樓梯亦加裝樓梯燈及加厚防撞墊；車上又會首次試用無線落車鐘。車廂內屏幕亦加入動態乘客資訊系統，畫面會交替顯示乘搭的路線號碼、未來5個站及全條行車路線資訊。<br />\n<br />\n譚稱，動態資訊系統亦會用於其他巴士，今年9月底前，會為其他375部巴士安裝，未來亦會嘗試在系統中加入到站的預計車程時間。<br />\n<br />\n九巴指，新車造價與其他巴士大致相若，因應服務需求，今年全年預計有約460架新車到港。目前車隊平均車齡由2014年的11年，降至去年7.5年，相信可減少故障率，而新車採用歐盟六期排放標準，有助減少污染物。<br />\n<br />\n發言人又指，港鐵沙中綫明年通車的競爭，預計影響將較觀塘延綫通車時嚴重，加上油價及人工成本上升，估計營運存在壓力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180416/large/a1101a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180416%2Flarge%2Fa1101a.gif&h=b50c426e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n豪華巴擬設留座服務<br />\n<br />\n港聞 4小時前"},{"pid":"4dbc82873171a8003164d3b0a58affce94ade6d7","tid":631179,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T08:45:05.000Z","msg":"坐過<br />\n民生野少有既進步"},{"pid":"a5727f30d17ff76491b31e76932afad815f5c94e","tid":631179,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T08:48:28.000Z","msg":"路線牌或會顯示動畫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd13b96e7cf44884381a8be2272d3eaa26d0c380","tid":631179,"uid":8636,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T09:07:58.000Z","msg":"整到咁豪華把鬼咩<br />\n不出一個月 咪又係比啲廢佬 大陸喱 中坑柒叔閪嬸 賤種蝗蝻童 MK狗<br />\n搞到架車污煙瘴氣"},{"pid":"9950d326ac1132d012ab50637b3f97d7875b075d","tid":631179,"uid":21035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5727f30d17ff76491b31e76932afad815f5c94e","tid":631179,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T08:48:28.000Z","msg":"路線牌或會顯示動畫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T09:14:15.000Z","msg":"做埋廣告位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}